{"tid":387671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"單車撚入","createTime":"2017-09-04T21:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T12:31:11.000Z","uid":72638,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22aa83a5da24d663d7e5fdd7c46d7a6b5e523274","tid":387671,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T21:48:07.000Z","msg":"我住市區九龍<br />\n想買架摺車<br />\n間中會坐港鐵入新界踩<br />\n<br />\n我170高7x公斤重<br />\n買16寸轆會唔會太細部？<br />\n因想慳位同方便攜帶<br />\n<br />\n想買dahon kaa672好唔好？<br />\n我應該唔會改車"},{"pid":"611cce7a528f5585d56f75b45b412200479607cc","tid":387671,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T22:06:06.000Z","msg":"冇人識？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9b29fc346e9aaff14b87621e3a6f4bc1f843ce","tid":387671,"uid":65320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T00:00:18.000Z","msg":"一步到位。小布啦"},{"pid":"ac32f78a29574ad4cefd4ac00aa287f166d69c5a","tid":387671,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一步到位。小布啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285449f55fa40b4e9c971b3512341e7dbe32d804","tid":387671,"uid":13878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:39:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一步到位。小布啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小布都叫一步到位...<br />\n<br />\n得個貴字, 唔通貴就好咩~6個波, 又唔夠快"},{"pid":"add5dc992054fb74c6400e88c42b3692a771f626","tid":387671,"uid":13878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:44:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我住市區九龍<br />\n想買架摺車<br />\n間中會坐港鐵入新界踩<br />\n<br />\n我170高7x公斤重<br />\n買16寸轆會唔會太細部？<br />\n因想慳位同方便攜帶<br />\n<br />\n想買dahon kaa672好唔好？<br />\n我應該唔會改車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n答番樓主問題先<br />\n<br />\n170 7Xcm<br />\n<br />\n如果你屋企唔係太細, 或者拎到番屋企根本唔洗摺都有位放既<br />\n個人建議買20寸<br />\n<br />\n因為個穩定性同速度差好遠~<br />\n<br />\n另外, DAHON大行, 係一個比較好既入門牌子~<br />\n佢有碟剎車款, 但個人建議唔需要<br />\n買番V剎就夠, 夠收, 易保養<br />\n<br />\n全車買番黎, 反而有幾樣野, 我覺得係值得升級換下既<br />\n1) 一體頭管, 可以令你架車強度增加, 穩陣好多<br />\n2) 大餅(即係踩果舊) <br />\n3) 換一張適合你既座墊<br />\n<br />\n咁其他野既, 用落先再諗啦。唔好晒無謂既錢"},{"pid":"cd60eabae6d9c19481281d9f0f13d1ecd0854897","tid":387671,"uid":44297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:44:53.000Z","msg":"留名買車"},{"pid":"a16c2606067aa203c01cdea7275828dd60368aba","tid":387671,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:47:31.000Z","msg":"電動板車好過啦"},{"pid":"f034f68f91967bc49c0ad6801faa9b95715b5aa6","tid":387671,"uid":35463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:42:17.000Z","msg":"個人建議買road bike<br />\n<br />\n輕啲 方便攜帶<br />\n摺車你摺幾次就唔會再摺<br />\nrb打企放/掛起都唔會好嘥位<br />\n<br />\n要架車好踩你先會有動力出車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53ec18a45dc5ccda249c0b8f3e6bea42d7b94d5","tid":387671,"uid":36100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:52:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人建議買road bike<br />\n<br />\n輕啲 方便攜帶<br />\n摺車你摺幾次就唔會再摺<br />\nrb打企放/掛起都唔會好嘥位<br />\n<br />\n要架車好踩你先會有動力出車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有心踩嘅，踩踩下就會變RB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c6f02f12bf958c6d414e1b419ff3dec3841124","tid":387671,"uid":36100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個人建議買road bike<br />\n<br />\n輕啲 方便攜帶<br />\n摺車你摺幾次就唔會再摺<br />\nrb打企放/掛起都唔會好嘥位<br />\n<br />\n要架車好踩你先會有動力出車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有心踩嘅，踩踩下就會變RB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔轉rb都會扮rb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc4b207239c04ba0997c3fb2c153db95fd98ed4","tid":387671,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0